OL,3,CHow hairdresser is styling a new
OL,4,Cfuture for Cavehill business
OL,6,FThere is a synergy between community,
OL,7,Fbusiness and positive spaces. It makes
OL,8,Fsense that an area that has attractive
OL,9,Fshop fronts, clean streets, cultural
OL,10,Fprojects that collective pride in that
OL,11,Farea rises.
OL,13,FIt's a fact which Paul Carlin, a
OL,14,Fhairdresser from north Belfast, was
OL,15,Fkeen to promote among the business
OL,16,Fcommunity and decision makers in that
OL,17,Fpart of the city.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
