OL,3,CHow hairdresser is styling a new
OL,4,Cfuture for Cavehill business
OL,6,FAs well as running his business on the
OL,7,FCavehill Road, he is the founder of
OL,8,Fthe Cavehill Business Association,
OL,9,Fhelped to establish the Cavehill
OL,10,FCommunity Choir which he still runs
OL,11,Fand is on the steering committee for
OL,12,Fthe Look North festival which starts
OL,13,Fthis weekend.
OL,15,FIn this week's Going the Extra Mile
OL,16,Fpodcast, Paul talks about his journey
OL,17,Ffrom establishing his own business to
OL,18,Fworking to develop business across
OL,19,Fnorth Belfast.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
