OL,3,CHow hairdresser is styling a new
OL,4,Cfuture for Cavehill business
OL,6,FPaul credits his mum with instilling
OL,7,Fthe desire to help others from an
OL,8,Fearly age.
OL,10,FLiving near Belfast Castle, he admits
OL,11,Fhis upbringing was in 'leafy Upper
OL,12,FAntrim Road' but his Mum worked with
OL,13,Fthe NSPCC, often with difficult cases,
OL,14,Fand exposed him to how others lived
OL,15,Fand urged him to 'count yourself
OL,16,Flucky' and it was that sense of
OL,17,Fappreciation which gave him the value
OL,18,Fsystem to work for himself and others.
OL,20,FAnd that is a value which Paul
OL,21,Fembodies.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
