OL,3,CHow hairdresser is styling a new
OL,4,Cfuture for Cavehill business
OL,6,FWhen it comes to community work,
OL,7,Fworking to develop local business and
OL,8,Findustry is not something that
OL,9,Fimmediately jumps out but as Paul
OL,10,Fsays, who wants to live in areas which
OL,11,Fare derelict or don't feel safe.
OL,13,FBy creating positive spaces, it
OL,14,Fencourages community.
OL,16,FWhen I asked Paul for Going the Extra
OL,17,FMile, what can people do to make a
OL,18,Fpositive difference in their
OL,19,Fcommunity, he was keen to emphasise
OL,20,Fthat while the big projects matter,
OL,21,Fthink small.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
