OL,3,CHow hairdresser is styling a new
OL,4,Cfuture for Cavehill business
OL,6,FThink of what will make people smile
OL,7,Fwhen they leave the house. Like Paul
OL,8,Fsays 'it's the wee stuff that affects
OL,9,Fmore people.'
